{"type":"article","id":1846,"title":"AO3防止菟杂满脸喷粪教程","uid":4355,"topics":[6,2002,2871],"contents":"本文将教各位膜友如何防止菟杂在文章平论区满脸喷粪<br>\n首先在文章发布时的privacy板块有enable comment moderation和disable anonymous comment功能：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/3oWScfQ.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3oWScfQ.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/3oWScfQ.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\nDAC发动后必须注册后登陆的用户才能发表平论<br>\nECM发动后必须文章作者审核后同意的言论才会显示在文章平论区<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/FbeNMSx.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FbeNMSx.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/FbeNMSx.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n如果已经发布的文章，也可以通过文章上方的edit设置来更改设置达到同样效果<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/SdJSV4Q.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SdJSV4Q.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SdJSV4Q.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n设置完毕后点post就可以了","date":"2020-04-18","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}